Installation instructions
-------------------------

Option 1 - Untar to your ~/.vim directory

Option 2 - Using pathogen (www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=2332):

    Untar/clone to ~/.vim/bundle/vimtodo/

Once installed, use :help vimtodo for more documentation, or see the
doc/todo.txt file.

